uSop69rG9-aoxa8C2nQ">Tiên trà thuỷ ký - 煎茶水記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%B1u-T%C3%A2n/author-MfG9Dcv0CtbGpIaXvmxDnA">Trương Hựu Tân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-Th%E1%BB%B1c/Ti%E1%BB%87p-d%C6%B0-o%C3%A1n/poem-QUKZTIYkWvyALfA9eRcDaQ">Tiệp dư oán - 婕妤怨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-L6pzAongjauOoKCOhSmVLw">Thôi Thực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-V%C4%A9nh/Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-mai-h%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-wos0o-d94iqF5FlL77AjzQ">Tuyết mai hương - 雪梅香</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-V%C4%A9nh/author-ODOFEl8xHVsWXQUPgj9Ktg">Liễu Vĩnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%C3%ADnh/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-UhSAHwICue2msChldw-DDA">Vô đề kỳ 3 - 無題其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%C3%ADnh/author-ZSJGdqhomRPBVjiE5QU4sQ">Trần Phương Bính</a>)<br></div>	</div>
